				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Level guide<a name="55373"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Aug 6 04 3:49 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I'm looking for the fastest leveling guide I can find for soloing 100% of the time and no swarm kiting. I would like to just melee/twist and charm kite my way solo as much as possible. If I have to swarm to kite my way through certain levels I will do it np but if there's a different option for soloing at that level i'd like that instead. 
<br />

<br />
Can anyone point me in the direction of such a guide? Or if one doesn't exist any suggestions? I know a lot of guides for leveling exist but a lot of them include grouping or just suggest swarm kiting 1-65, and i'd like to avoid that.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
