				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Level guide<a name="55392"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Aug 6 04 8:25 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I am sure there are tips to be gained through the guides already written but I can add a little maybe. Go to Eqatlas and study the hunting guides. I personally look for a zone with levels even and below me and then go take a look at the zone.  I look for a decent area to have some room to run and then I just have fun. 
<br />

<br />
I do not do the swarm or ae kiting, I find it much more fun to pull in 3 or 4 blues and then run around under their feet yelling Nyah Nyahh until all are dead. I use a mixture of charming and just chants with slow (to conserve mana) and I find I can hunt all night and have an absolute blast.
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
</span></td>
