				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Level guide<a name="55395"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Aug 6 04 8:44 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Look to the left and click on the Guides link.  Everything you need to know, from fear kiting to AoE kiting to swarm kiting is there.  Now, for where to hunt, here is the route I went.
<br />

<br />
1-4:  Newbie yard trash by your starting city- Solo Melee
<br />
5-8:  Orc Hill Greater Fay- Solo Melee (do CB belt quest)
<br />
6-12:  Clan Crushbone - Solo Melee(do CB belt and Shoulderpad quest)
<br />
12-18: Unrest-Everything in the yard - Solo AoE Kiting
<br />
18-22:  Paludal Caverns - Shriks - Solo AoE Kiting
<br />
22-27:  Marus Seru - Greyhoppers and Stonegrabber - Solo AoE Kiting
<br />
27-32:  Iceclad - Snow Cougars - Solo AoE Kiting
<br />
32-43:  Gulf of Gunthak - Undead - Solo AoE Kiting
<br />
43-48:  Dulak's Harbor - Broken Skull scouts - Solo AoE Kiting
<br />
48-53:  Dulak's Harbor - anything blue - Solo Swarm Kiiting
<br />
53-55:  Dulak's Harbor - Armory &amp; Orcencrasher - Solo AoE Kiting
<br />
55-57:  Plane of Nightmare - Ravenous Nightstalkers - Solo Swarm Kiting
<br />

<br />
Hope this helps!!
<br />

<br />

<br />
</span></td>
