				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Level guide<a name="55399"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Aug 6 04 9:02 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span> I started a Ranger mainly as a spare tracker. He is currently lvl 30. I can tell you where I went and the xp was very good. 1-4 in any newbie area. 5-9 or 10 Crushbone. 10-16 in Kurns Tower. 16-22 or 23 Paludal Caverns. 23-30 Mistmoore Castle. Note that CB, Kurns,PC and MM have HUGE xp bonuses about double xp per kill than normal zones. Also the mobs are very easy and low HP's. I flew through the first 30 lvls solo but twinked with a fungi and decent weapons. The xp is still good at 30 in MM but I may try Tower of frozen shadow, a bigger xp bonus may have been added there much like MM.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
