				<td colspan="2"><span>Don't forget to look through the <a target="_new" href="http://www.eqdiva.com/eq/hunting.aspx">Hunting Archive</a> here on EQDiva. The information is old(early 2000 and on) but a lot of it, especially between 1-50, is still applicable.
<br />

<br />
Also, EQdiva provides <a target="_new" href="http://www.eqdiva.com/eq/zoneLevels.aspx">zone exp mod lists</a> and zone mob levels to give you an idea of what to expect in certain zones. When leveling my alts I find it useful to pick out a couple zones with the level of content suitable to my alt and go have fun in zones I don't usually go to(like Dalnir, very fun zone).</span></td>
